info.title: Borsdata API v1.0
info.description:
Get access to Nordic Stockmarket - Instruments, Reports and KPIs. </br>   
                For Nordic Market you need Pro membership.
                </br>
                API BaseUrl is : https://apiservice.borsdata.se  </br> 
                On  GitHub you find test-client, Wiki and Tickets </br>  
                https://github.com/Borsdata-Sweden </br>
